Odaily Planet Daily News Trump announced the schedule for "Liberation Day" (April 2, 2025, local time in the United States): 
1. 9:00 a.m. Eastern Time (21:00 Beijing Time on April 2): ​​President Trump held a meeting with his expert trade committee to finalize the transformative tariff measures; 
2. 11:30 a.m. Eastern Time (23:30 Beijing Time on April 2): ​​Press Secretary Karoline Leavitt previewed the statement; 
3. 4:00 p.m. Eastern Time (4:00 a.m. Beijing Time on April 3): Rose Garden speech-Trump will announce reciprocal tariffs; 
4. 4:30 p.m. Eastern Time (4:30 a.m. Beijing Time on April 3): Contact with the media, followed by a formal photo; 
5. 6:00 p.m. Eastern Time (6:00 a.m. Beijing Time on April 3): Government officials briefed industry leaders on the implementation to ensure seamless execution; 
6. Evening Eastern Time 8:00 (8:00 a.m. Beijing time, April 3): Global markets react.
